Ing '''Saint Louis University''' (SLU) metung yang pipagaralan king [[Baguio Lakanbalen]] a manga aduang dalan limampulung (250) kilometru king pangulu ning [[Menila]].

==Pekamaulagang impormasiun==

Tetag de kanitang 1911 deng misionariu ning [[w:Congregatio Immaculati Cordis Mariae]] (CICM) ing Saint Louis University ba yang isundu ing pamag-Cristianu na ning pangulu ning Filipinas. Mayayakit ya king [[Baguio Lakanbalen]], metung a siudad bakasiunan aduang dalan limampulung (250) kilometru king pangulu ning [[Menila]] a ausan dang "Summer Capital of the Philippines"  (Kapitoliung Pangkaleldo ning Filipinas). Ing SLU ing pekamaragul a unibersidad king [[Cordillera Administrative Region|Pangulung Filipinas]] (Northern Philippines); kanitang Noviembri 17, 2007, 20,750 (adua lang pulung libu pitung dalan limang pulu) la reng magaral keti, at ibat la karen ngang labuad ning Filipinas deti, bukud pa kareng aliwang bangsa. Atyu king sentru ning Baguio ing kayang campus a maki atlung pulung gusali, at misasamut la keti deng miyayaliwang kultura ampong nasiun. Ngeni, tuturing deng metung kareng manimuna at gagalang a institusion ning Filipinas. Daragul ya kayabe ing pamangailangan da reng magaral ampong talaturu, at miyayampang yang pamagaral king elementaria sekundaria, kolehiyu ampong graduadu.         

===Amlat===

Kanitang 1907, míras la king Filipinas deng misionariung CICM, a tiburan ning Vaticanung gawan yang Cristianu ing dake nang pangulu ning bangsa. King Baguio la menuknangan deting misionariu uling pareu yang malapit iti king Menila ampo king lalawigan ning Benguet king kabundukang [[Cordillera]], nung nu maki dakal a tribung tubu. Aniang 1911, tetag neng Rev. Fr. Séraphin Devesse, CICM king Baguio para kareng apulung ának a lalaking taga karin, at inaus neng '''Saint Louis School''' iti. Ketang 1915, meragul ya ing eskuela, at megi yang vocational and trade school, at mitikdo yang sanga iti. Aniang banuang 1952, mibusni ya ing College of Liberal Arts and Commerce, kapamilata’nang Gerard Decaestecker. Kalabas ning panaun, miragdagan la reng kayang kursu at sinulung ya ing pipagaralan. Mekilala la reng programa nang pang-graduadu ning Saint Louis College ketang 1955, at megi yang unibersidad kanitang 1963.<ref>[http://www.slu.edu.ph/about/history.jsp Saint Louis University, Baguio City, Philippines<!-- Bot generated title -->]</ref>
 
Mika ranggu yang katlu kareng aduang dalan siam a pulu’t anam a eskuela king mabilug a Filipinas basi king bilang da reng mipapasar kareng miyayaliwang iksamin manibat 1999 anggang 2003 agpang king pamanyuri ning Professional Regulation Commission ampo ing Commission on Higher Education.  

===Ing Banua-banuang Pamanalkus ning SLU===
*1907 Miras la king Filipinas deng misionariung CICM king tubud ning Santa Sede (Holy See) ba yang gawang Cristianu ing pangulu nang dake ning bangsa 
*1911 Mipaltutu ing paninap nang Rev. Fr. Serafino De Vesse, CICM aniang tetag ne ing St. Louis Mission School, king malating baleng metung mu kuartu, a maki apulung disipulus.
*1915 Megi yang trade school ing St. Louis Louis lalam nang Fr. Florimond Carlu. Kasaup la reng Canonesses of St. Augustine, megi yang kumpletung eskuelang pang-primaria, a maki gradung intermediate 
*1921 Mipalagyuan yang St. Louis School ing eskuela, a pekilagyu ra kang San [[Luis Gonzaga]]. Meragul ya iti at mika sekundaria: saparadu ya ing campus king Cathedral Hill para kareng sekundariang lálaki, at maki sarili no man deng bábaing sekundaria ampong elementaria king Campo Filipino.   
*1951 Kaibat ning Kaduang Gerang Meto Yatu, mibuklat yang pasibayu ing eskuela, busal ning kasiran. Deng Misionariung CICM ing menibala ketang Boys’ High School, kabang madre no mang ICM deng tinalan king Girls High School
*1952 Uli ning misanib a pamagmalasakit da ri Msgr. William Brasseur ampong Rev. Fr. Rafael Desmedt, mitátag ya ing Saint Louis College, a kanita bibilugan da makatuking departamentu: Education, Liberal Arts, Commerce and Secretarial. Pitung pulu’t lima (75) la mu deng magaral aniang migumpisa ya ing eskuela.  
*1954 Migumpisa ya ing College of Engineering ampo ing College of Law 
*1956 Mitikdo ya ing Graduate School of Arts and Sciences
*1963 Mipalagyuan yang Saint Louis University ing Saint Louis College aniang pigkalubanan ne king kabilian a unibersidad ning kapamahalan ning Filipinas kanitang May 16, 1963. Ing SLU ing mumunang pribadung unibersidad king pangulung Filipinas a mekilalang unibersidad.
*1967 Megi yang aduang kolehiyu, ing College of Human Sciences ampong College of Natural Sciences, ing College of Liberal Arts.
*1976 Mitátag ya ing College of Medicine ampo ing College of Nursing.
*1977 Mitikdo ya ing SLU Hospital of the Sacred Heart bang sumuyu king pamangailangan dang pangkabulasan deng memalen ning Baguio. Iti ing pipagsanayan da reng magaral king College of Medicine ampong College of Nursing.
*1982 Kaibat ning maigpit a pamanyuri, pigkalubanan ne king kabilian a “deregulated” (sariling pamanibala) ning Philippine Association of Accrediting Schools, Colleges and Universities (PAASCU) ing SLU.
*1983 Miyari ya ing Dr. Waldo S. Perfecto Building
*1986 Milukluk ya i Rev. Fr. Joseph Van Den Daelen, CICM
*1986 Pigmasusian na ning SLU ing pitumpulu’t limang (75) banua ketang kayang Diamond Jubilee Year, a maki temang “Sharing Wisdom Building Values for God and Country.”. 
*1990 Migumpisa ya ing Institute for Information and Computer Science (IICS)
*1993 Mitátag ya ing Center for Culture and the Arts aniang Mayu 27.
*1994 Megi yang College of Information and Computing Sciences ing IICS
*1996 Miyari ya ing Covered Court

